WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.790 --> 00:00:04.190
&gt;&gt; From the Library of
Congress in Washington, DC.

00:00:04.190 --> 00:00:08.290
&gt;&gt; Courtney Dell: As a
mom of three young kids,

00:00:08.290 --> 00:00:12.930
we love Doreen Cronin
and Betsy Lewin's books.

00:00:12.930 --> 00:00:14.750
They're a staple in
our house and have been

00:00:14.750 --> 00:00:17.000
since before we actually
had children.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:20.250
Doreen Cronin is a lawyer turned
full-time children's book author,

00:00:20.250 --> 00:00:24.400
and Betsy Lewin got her start in
illustration and greeting cards.

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:27.900
Together, they've collaborated
on a number of projects all

00:00:27.900 --> 00:00:31.330
with witty themes and
beautiful illustrations,

00:00:31.330 --> 00:00:33.960
and their most recent collaboration
is "Click, Clack, Surprise"

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:36.940
and with that, I'll
turn it over to them.

00:00:36.940 --> 00:00:38.640
&gt;&gt; Thank you.

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:41.040
[ Applause ]

00:00:41.040 --> 00:00:42.340
&gt;&gt; Betsy Lewin: Good morning.

00:00:42.340 --> 00:00:45.100
&gt;&gt; Doreen Cronin: Thank you all
for coming out this morning.

00:00:45.100 --> 00:00:47.710
Betsy and I are excited to be here.

00:00:47.710 --> 00:00:53.890
Betsy and I have been working
together for over 15 years

00:00:53.890 --> 00:00:57.040
so we have been together
for a long, long time.

00:00:57.040 --> 00:00:59.280
We've done quite a
few books together.

00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:00.580
Let me see if they come.

00:01:00.580 --> 00:01:01.880
There we go.

00:01:01.880 --> 00:01:05.300
So, we like to visit
a lot of schools.

00:01:05.300 --> 00:01:06.670
We like to go out on book tour.

00:01:06.670 --> 00:01:09.910
We like to come to conventions
and mostly read to the kids.

00:01:09.910 --> 00:01:11.410
That's the best part.

00:01:11.410 --> 00:01:12.710
Writing is great.

00:01:12.710 --> 00:01:15.250
I'm sure illustrating
is great but reading

00:01:15.250 --> 00:01:17.340 position:56%
with kids is the absolute best part.

00:01:17.340 --> 00:01:19.700
A lot of the books that we
do like "Click Clack Moo"

00:01:19.700 --> 00:01:23.220
"Click Clack Peep"
"Click Clack Boo."

00:01:23.220 --> 00:01:25.450
We like to put a lot
of sounds in there.

00:01:25.450 --> 00:01:26.930
There's movement in there.

00:01:26.930 --> 00:01:29.050
So, kids, if you're out there
and you want to make sounds,

00:01:29.050 --> 00:01:32.110 position:56%
then make some sounds, and if you
want to get up and you want to move,

00:01:32.110 --> 00:01:36.020 position:56%
you know, be respectful of your
space but you don't have to be quiet

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:39.240
and sit perfectly when
you read, okay?

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:44.620
When you read, you can be animated
and join in and say what you need

00:01:44.620 --> 00:01:47.300
