was an extremely introverted child.

00:24:06.790 --> 00:24:10.360
I talked at home with my brothers,
my sisters, and my friends

00:24:10.360 --> 00:24:13.140
but you put me in a classroom
and I was extremely quiet.

00:24:13.140 --> 00:24:14.590
I was just a very, very quiet kid.

00:24:14.590 --> 00:24:15.940
Very shy kid.

00:24:15.940 --> 00:24:19.010
But my first grade teacher,

00:24:19.010 --> 00:24:21.640
quiet doesn't mean you
have nothing to say.

00:24:21.640 --> 00:24:25.310
Quiet doesn't mean you have nothing
to add so she said to me, "Well,

00:24:25.310 --> 00:24:27.430
why don't you start writing
things down because I want

00:24:27.430 --> 00:24:30.950
to hear what you have to say,"
and she gave me extra homework.

00:24:30.950 --> 00:24:33.890 position:56%
I was six, and my first grade
teacher was giving me extra homework

00:24:33.890 --> 00:24:35.190
to write.

00:24:35.190 --> 00:24:38.740
And so, she saw something in
me that I was more comfortable

00:24:38.740 --> 00:24:43.170
and probably still am to this
day writing than I am talking.

00:24:43.170 --> 00:24:46.110
I'd rather write all day then
talk all day and she saw that.

00:24:46.110 --> 00:24:48.290
And so, she just encouraged
me to keep writing and then

00:24:48.290 --> 00:24:49.590
as it happened some of the stuff

00:24:49.590 --> 00:24:52.600
that I was writing,
she felt was good.

00:24:52.600 --> 00:24:56.730 position:56%
Was saying that maybe I was a writer
and so she'd give me poems to write

00:24:56.730 --> 00:24:59.710
and give me short stories to
write and all this extra stuff

00:24:59.710 --> 00:25:01.460
that I had to do but I loved it.

00:25:01.460 --> 00:25:02.760
I absolutely loved it.

00:25:02.760 --> 00:25:07.390
And so, when I was six, I had a
teacher who I adored say to me,

00:25:07.390 --> 00:25:10.580
"You are a writer," and
that was all it took.

00:25:10.580 --> 00:25:13.240
