different challenges

00:25:18.500 --> 00:25:20.100
and learning new things
and then college.

00:25:20.100 --> 00:25:23.930
I was a journalism major
because I was a writer.

00:25:23.930 --> 00:25:26.060
And then I went to law
school a few years later

00:25:26.060 --> 00:25:28.940
because lawyers read
a lot and write a lot.

00:25:28.940 --> 00:25:30.700
So, I went to law school.

00:25:30.700 --> 00:25:34.020
One of the reasons was
because I was a writer.

00:25:34.020 --> 00:25:36.890
It just became part of my
identity and that was it.

00:25:36.890 --> 00:25:38.920
And that started --
that was a teacher.

00:25:38.920 --> 00:25:40.900
